de.mslab.diffbuilder.DifferenceBuilder

  • Packages that use DifferenceBuilder 
    Package Description
    de.mslab.bicliquesearch
    Provides classes which implement the biclique finding process.
    de.mslab.diffbuilder
    Provides helper classes which are required for biclique creation, such as to construct differences for bit-wise or byte-wise operating ciphers, or to compare differentials for their independency.

      class  BytewiseDifferenceBuilder
